to send messages(packets)
  ping "ip address of receiver pc"

eg: ping 10.0.0.2



  FOR REFRENCE ONLY

switch commands:

  click : CLI

now enter following commands in IOS Command Line interface :- 

enable 
conf -t
vlan 2
name office
exit 
vlan 3
name home
exit 
interface fastEthernet 0/1
switch access vlan 2
  exit
  interface fastEthernet 0/2
switch access vlan 2
  exit
  interface fastEthernet 0/3
switch access vlan 3
  exit
  interface fastEthernet 0/4
switch access vlan 4
  exit

  
  


